name: Whiteboard
body:
# Demo

Just a test for the updated versions of the libraries working with the latest code.

The demo starts with two squares that can be moved on a 10x10 section grid, rotated and resized.

[Latest version](demo/index.html) (v0.0.1)

## Libraries

Demo is currently running:
* Fabric.js 1.4.13
* jQuery 2.1.1
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
